<HEADLINE>
<P>
ATHLETE OF THE WEEK: BOYS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jarron Collins 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Harvard-Westlake 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Basketball 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Freshman 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: Collins and his twin brother Jason have started their high 
school careers impressively, leading the Wolverines to a 16-1 record.Jarron is 
averaging 10.1 points and 7.9 rebounds. 
</P>
<P>
 WEEK AT A GLANCE: Collins scored 18 points in a 63-58 victory Friday at Bishop 
Montgomery. Collins' grandfather died Jan. 16 and the earthquake damaged his 
home in Granada Hills, causing the family to spend a night in a van. "It was 
hard," Collins said. "I didn't feel like playing a basketball game." 
</P>
