DATA ON MOLESTERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * What a brilliant idea the California attorney general has hatched ("Lungren 
Urges Molester Data in Libraries," Jan. 12). Indeed, let us post child-molester 
data in all the county libraries.The problem is that many libraries are closed, 
some permanently. 
</P>
