<P>
 Red Cross Service Centers 
</P>
<P>
 These Red Cross service centers opened Tuesday. Caseworkers can assess 
disaster-caused needs and provide vouchers for food, clothing, temporary 
housing and rental assistance, help with health and medical needs, urgent 
household items such as bedding or cookware and some home repairs. Those who 
cannot be seen the same day will be given an appointment and asked to return in 
the next day or two. Hours are 9 a.m. to 7 p.m. until further notice. 
</P>
<P>
 * Bethlehem Lutheran Church, 27265 Luther Drive, Santa Clarita 
</P>
<P>
 * Epiphany Lutheran Church, 7769 Topanga Canyon Road, Canoga Park 
</P>
<P>
 * Fillmore Senior Center, 533 Santa Clara Ave. 
</P>
<P>
 * First United Methodist Church of San Fernando, 1525 Glenoaks Blvd. 
