</P>
<P>
 Water will be available from 7 a.m. to 9 p.m. at the following locations. 
Recipients must bring their own clean containers. There is no limit; trucks 
refill and return to sites throughout the day. Ice trucks will make rounds 
today at noon at the five locations in bold: 
