Legal Aid 
</P>
<P>
 The Los Angeles County Bar Assn's Lawyer Referral and Information Service has 
added four new messages to its Smartlaw Legal Information line. The free 
messages discuss insurance, debt, employment, and health care concerns and 
operates 24 hours. (213) 243-1500. 
</P>
<P>
 If you need to hire an attorney, the Lawyer Referral and Information Service 
is waiving its usual $25 fee and offering earthquake victims up to half-hour 
free consultations with participating attorneys. Call (213) 243-1525 on 
weekdays, 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
