<HEADLINE>
<P>
MIKE DOWNEY: A RINGING TESTAMENT TO NEW BOSS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MIKE DOWNEY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A bus pulls up to Fox television's first football game and out steps John 
Madden. September, 1994. 
</P>
<P>
 "OK! Let's earn that money! There's the kickoff! BOOM! That was some kick, 
Pat!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure was, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "WHAM! Good kick! So how much I make there? Ten thousand bucks? KA-CHING! Did 
you hear that cash register, Pat?" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure did, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "I'll tell ya!" 
</P>
<P>
 "First and 10, Cowboys." 
</P>
<P>
 "This is a BIG play, Pat! Even though it's still EARLY, I mean! KA-CHING! 
Twenty thousand dollars!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Aikman . . ." 
</P>
<P>
 "This is SOME game, Pat!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Complete to Irvin." 
</P>
<P>
 "OK! Let's look at that play AGAIN, Pat! KA-CHING! Thirty thousand!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Good for a Dallas first down." 
</P>
<P>
 "I'll tell ya!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Show us that play, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "OK! Irvin lines up HERE! He runs HERE! He catches the ball HERE! And BING 
BANG BOOM! Right on the MONEY, Pat!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Right you are, John Madden." 
</P>
<P>
 "I'll tell ya!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Second down, Dallas. . . ." 
</P>
<P>
 "KA-CHING! I've already made 40 thousand BUCKS here! How much YOU made so far, 
Pat?" 
</P>
<P>
 "Not sure, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "Ten thou? Twenty thou?" 
</P>
<P>
 "Aikman hands off to Smith." 
</P>
<P>
 "POW! Emmitt really got POPPED!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure did, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "That was SOME hit, Pat!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure was, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "I'll tell ya!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Time out, Dallas." 
</P>
<P>
 "Let's look at that hit AGAIN, Pat! Smith lines up HERE! Then he runs HERE! 
And WHAM BOOM BAM! He ain't goin' no place, Pat! KA-CHING! Fifty thousand!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Good drawing, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "Got his bell RUNG, Pat!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure did, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "I'll tell ya!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Right you are, John Madden." 
</P>
<P>
 "KA-CHING! Eighty thousand!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Dallas will have to punt." 
</P>
<P>
 "This is SOME kind of ballgame, Pat! 
</P>
<P>
 "Wait, they're going for it on fourth down, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "This is a GUTSY play, Pat!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure is, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "I'll tell ya!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Correction. It's only third down." 
</P>
<P>
 "Don't MATTER, Pat! We still get PAID! KA-CHING!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure do, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "We don't gotta do NOTHIN' but sit here!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Sure don't, John." 
</P>
<P>
 "We ain't even gotta talk good English!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Right you are, John Madden." 
</P>
<P>
 "KA-CHING! A hun-derd thousand!" 
</P>
<P>
 "Aikman. . . ." 
</P>
<P>
 "What about him?" 
</P>
<P>
 "Back to pass." 
</P>
<P>
 "Oh!" 
</P>
