 "Right you are, John Madden." 
</P>
<P>
 "Let's look at that play AGAIN, Pat! This guy lines up HERE! This guy lines up 
THERE! That guy runs up HERE! This other guy crosses over THERE! BIFF BAM BOOM! 
And down he GOES!" 
</P>
