north and Garden Grove Boulevard on the south; and Western Avenue on the west 
and Nutwood Street on the east. 
</P>
<P>
 "People think tire slashing is not a heinous crime, but a lot of people trying 
to get to work were inconvenienced," said Sgt. George Jaramillo, 
