</P>
<P>
 * Venice Blvd. at Interstate 10, closed from Cadillac Ave. to La Cienega Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
 * La Cienega Blvd. at Interstate 10 (open southbound to I-10 on-ramp, closed 
under freeway to Venice Blvd.; northbound closed from Venice Blvd. to Cadillac 
Ave.) 
</P>
<P>
