<HEADLINE>
<P>
LEE DUBRIDGE FUNERAL TO BE HELD THURSDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Funeral services for Lee A. DuBridge, former president of Caltech who died 
Sunday at the age of 92, will be conducted at 11 a.m. Thursday at the Pasadena 
Presbyterian Church, Colorado Boulevard and Madison Avenue, Pasadena. Caltech 
is also planning a later memorial service for DuBridge, who served as science 
adviser to President Richard M. Nixon. 
</P>
</TEXT>
