<DOCNO> LA012694-0186 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 007315 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 26, 1994, Wednesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
