<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rainbow Technologies Inc.: The supplier of personal computer security devices 
said it has formed a new unit, Rainbow Technologies Ltd.Canada, and has 
acquired the assets of AND Group Inc. of Calgary, Alberta. Terms were not 
disclosed. 
</P>
<P>
 The AND Group has developed technology for the secure delivery of information 
and software via CD-ROM, according to Rainbow, which has been marketing this 
product as the VendorSystem. Rainbow said it has licensed VendorSystem to 
companies such as Apple Computer, Ingram Micro, Aldus Corp., KidSoft and other 
major software publishers. 
</P>
